      <title>Ubuntu搭建Django+VUE开发环境</title>
      <link href="/2024/01/26/Ubuntu%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BADjango+VUE%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
      <url>/2024/01/26/Ubuntu%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BADjango+VUE%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Ubuntu搭建Django-VUE开发环境"><a href="#Ubuntu搭建Django-VUE开发环境" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu搭建Django+VUE开发环境"></a>Ubuntu搭建Django+VUE开发环境</h1><blockquote><p>最近打算写一个项目使用Django写API，VUE写前端，故打算在Ubuntu上搭建一套开发环境</p></blockquote><p>‍</p><h1 id="安装Mysql"><a href="#安装Mysql" class="headerlink" title="安装Mysql"></a>安装Mysql</h1><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install mysql-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><h2 id="验证mysql安装"><a href="#验证mysql安装" class="headerlink" title="验证mysql安装"></a>验证mysql安装</h2><p> <strong>mysql -u root -p</strong></p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261050771.png">​</p></li><li><h2 id="更改mysql-root密码"><a href="#更改mysql-root密码" class="headerlink" title="更改mysql root密码"></a>更改mysql root密码</h2><p> <strong>sudo mysql</strong> 进入mysql bash</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261050274.png">​</p><p> <strong>use mysql;</strong></p><p> <strong>ALTER USER ‘root‘@’localhost’ IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY ‘新密码’</strong> ;</p><p> 此时可以用新密码 通过 <strong>mysql -u root -p</strong> 进行登录</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261050826.png">​</p></li></ol><p>‍</p><h1 id="安装Python"><a href="#安装Python" class="headerlink" title="安装Python"></a>安装Python</h1><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Ubuntu 22.04 默认自带了Python3 ，但是没有pip，我们需要自行安装</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><h2 id="安装pip"><a href="#安装pip" class="headerlink" title="安装pip"></a>安装pip</h2><p> 当前环境无pip</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261050229.png">​</p><p> <strong>sudo apt-get update</strong></p><p> <strong>sudo apt install python3-pip</strong>​</p></li><li><h2 id="验证pip安装"><a href="#验证pip安装" class="headerlink" title="验证pip安装"></a>验证pip安装</h2><p> <strong>pip –version</strong></p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261051287.png">​</p></li></ol><p>‍</p><h1 id="安装Docker"><a href="#安装Docker" class="headerlink" title="安装Docker"></a>安装Docker</h1><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install docker</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install docker-compose</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><h2 id="验证docker安装"><a href="#验证docker安装" class="headerlink" title="验证docker安装"></a>验证docker安装</h2><p> <strong>docker –version</strong></p><p> <strong>docker-compose –version</strong></p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261051322.png">​</p></li><li><h2 id="在Docker中启动多版本mysql"><a href="#在Docker中启动多版本mysql" class="headerlink" title="在Docker中启动多版本mysql"></a>在Docker中启动多版本mysql</h2><p> mysql 8</p> <figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> mysql 5</p> <figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>‍</p><h1 id="安装Django"><a href="#安装Django" class="headerlink" title="安装Django"></a>安装Django</h1><blockquote><p>由于我是项目迁移，之前已经写好了部分代码，给关于Django编写API详细步骤未做记录，只记录迁移时遇到的问题</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pip3 install django</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><h2 id="No-module-named-‘corsheaders’"><a href="#No-module-named-‘corsheaders’" class="headerlink" title="No module named ‘corsheaders’"></a>No module named ‘corsheaders’</h2><p> ​<code>pip install django-cors-headers</code>​</p></li><li><h2 id="No-module-named-‘rest-framework’"><a href="#No-module-named-‘rest-framework’" class="headerlink" title="No module named ‘rest_framework’"></a>No module named ‘rest_framework’</h2><p> ​<code>pip install djangorestframework</code>​</p></li><li><h2 id="Did-you-install-mysqlclient"><a href="#Did-you-install-mysqlclient" class="headerlink" title="Did you install mysqlclient?"></a>Did you install mysqlclient?</h2><p> ​<code>pip3 install pymysql</code>​</p><p> 在settings.py 同级目录的 <strong>init</strong>.py 添加如下代码</p> <figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import pymysql</span><br><span class="line">pymysql.install_as_MySQLdb()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h2 id="No-module-named-‘rest-framework-simplejwt’"><a href="#No-module-named-‘rest-framework-simplejwt’" class="headerlink" title="No module named ‘rest_framework_simplejwt’"></a>No module named ‘rest_framework_simplejwt’</h2><p> ​<code>pip install djangorestframework-simplejwt -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</code>​</p></li><li><h2 id="No-module-named-‘pandas’"><a href="#No-module-named-‘pandas’" class="headerlink" title="No module named ‘pandas’"></a>No module named ‘pandas’</h2><p> ​<code>pip install pandas</code>​</p></li><li><h2 id="django-db-utils-OperationalError-1049-“Unknown-database-xx"><a href="#django-db-utils-OperationalError-1049-“Unknown-database-xx" class="headerlink" title="django.db.utils.OperationalError: (1049, “Unknown database xx)"></a>django.db.utils.OperationalError: (1049, “Unknown database xx)</h2><p> 创建对应数据库</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261051233.png">​</p></li><li><h2 id="应用迁移"><a href="#应用迁移" class="headerlink" title="应用迁移"></a>应用迁移</h2><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261051329.png">​</p><p> ​<code>python manage.py makemigrations</code>​</p><p> ​<code>python manage.py migrate</code>​</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261051790.png">​</p></li><li><p>启动Django项目</p><p> ​<code>python3 manage.py runserver 8001</code>​</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261051300.png">​</p></li></ol><p>‍</p><h1 id="安装VUE"><a href="#安装VUE" class="headerlink" title="安装VUE"></a>安装VUE</h1><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install @vue/cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><h2 id="验证VUE安装"><a href="#验证VUE安装" class="headerlink" title="验证VUE安装"></a>验证VUE安装</h2><p> ​<code>vue -V</code>​</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261052310.png">​</p></li><li><h2 id="启动VUE项目"><a href="#启动VUE项目" class="headerlink" title="启动VUE项目"></a>启动VUE项目</h2><p> 权限报错解决</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261052694.png">​</p><p> ​<code>chmod 777 node_modules/.bin/vue-cli-service</code>​</p><p> ​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401261052454.png">​</p></li></ol><p>‍</p>]]></content>
      
      
