      <title>Regolith3.0打造扁平化Ubuntu</title>
      <link href="/2024/01/25/Ubuntu%20Regolith%203.0%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/"/>
      <url>/2024/01/25/Ubuntu%20Regolith%203.0%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Ubuntu-Regolith-3-0设置"><a href="#Ubuntu-Regolith-3-0设置" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu Regolith 3.0设置"></a>Ubuntu Regolith 3.0设置</h1><h1 id="安装-Regolith3-0"><a href="#安装-Regolith3-0" class="headerlink" title="安装 Regolith3.0"></a>安装 Regolith3.0</h1><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">官网</span><br><span class="line">https://regolith-desktop.com/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>打造扁平化Ubuntu</p></blockquote><p>‍</p><h1 id="更换国内源"><a href="#更换国内源" class="headerlink" title="更换国内源"></a>更换国内源</h1><p>备份官方源</p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo cp /etc/apt/sources.list /etc/apt/sources.list.backup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更换国内源</p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim/etc/apt/sources.list</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">添加以下内容</span><br><span class="line"># 默认注释了源码镜像以提高 apt update 速度，如有需要可自行取消注释</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 预发布软件源，不建议启用</span><br><span class="line"># deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ jammy-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更新</p><p>​<code>sudo apt update</code>​</p><h2 id="换源后更新报错"><a href="#换源后更新报错" class="headerlink" title="换源后更新报错"></a>换源后更新报错</h2><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241715439.png">​</p><h2 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h2><p>vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;systemd&#x2F;resolved.conf</p><p>dns改成8.8.8.8</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241715224.png">​</p><p>保存后重启</p><p>‍</p><h1 id="安装Regolith外观"><a href="#安装Regolith外观" class="headerlink" title="安装Regolith外观"></a>安装Regolith外观</h1><p>详细请参考</p><p>​<code>https://regolith-desktop.com/docs/using-regolith/configuration/</code>​</p><h2 id="安装所有外观"><a href="#安装所有外观" class="headerlink" title="安装所有外观"></a>安装所有外观</h2><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install regolith-look-*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="切换外观"><a href="#切换外观" class="headerlink" title="切换外观"></a>切换外观</h2><p>​<code>super（windows下的win键） + alt + l</code>​</p><p>切换为自己喜欢的即可</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241715390.png">​</p><p>‍</p><h1 id="设置中文"><a href="#设置中文" class="headerlink" title="设置中文"></a>设置中文</h1><p>​<code>super + 空格 </code>​</p><p>打开设置</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716254.png">​</p><h2 id="下载中文语言包"><a href="#下载中文语言包" class="headerlink" title="下载中文语言包"></a>下载中文语言包</h2><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716304.png">​</p><p>选择中文</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716262.png">​</p><p>建议保留英文</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716734.png">​</p><h2 id="注销后重新登录界面已经变成中文"><a href="#注销后重新登录界面已经变成中文" class="headerlink" title="注销后重新登录界面已经变成中文"></a>注销后重新登录界面已经变成中文</h2><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716323.png">​</p><p>‍</p><h1 id="设置中文输入法"><a href="#设置中文输入法" class="headerlink" title="设置中文输入法"></a>设置中文输入法</h1><p>设置-&gt;键盘</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716403.png">​</p><p>移除汉语</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716372.png">​</p><h2 id="切换输入法"><a href="#切换输入法" class="headerlink" title="切换输入法"></a>切换输入法</h2><p>此时可以通过 SHIFT键切换中英文输入</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716983.png">​</p><p>‍</p><h1 id="oh-my-zsh-配置"><a href="#oh-my-zsh-配置" class="headerlink" title="oh my zsh 配置"></a>oh my zsh 配置</h1><h2 id="安装zsh"><a href="#安装zsh" class="headerlink" title="安装zsh"></a>安装zsh</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在bash中输入 zsh 即可进入 zsh，但是此时 通过 <code>echo $SHELL</code>​ 发现默认还是bash</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241716466.png">​</p><h2 id="安装oh-my-zsh"><a href="#安装oh-my-zsh" class="headerlink" title="安装oh my zsh"></a>安装oh my zsh</h2><p>需要先安装git</p><p>​<code>sudo apt install git</code>​</p><p>需要自行配置科学上网</p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241717409.png">​</p><p>更改默认shell</p><p>​<code>chsh -s $(which zsh)</code>​</p><p>注销后再打开终端发现默认为 zsh</p><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241717077.png">​</p><h2 id="安装ohmyzsh插件"><a href="#安装ohmyzsh插件" class="headerlink" title="安装ohmyzsh插件"></a>安装ohmyzsh插件</h2><h3 id="安装插件z"><a href="#安装插件z" class="headerlink" title="安装插件z"></a>安装插件<strong>z</strong></h3><p>Z是一个快捷路径跳转插件，输入z 通过 tab可以快捷选择曾经访问过的路径</p><p>​<code>vim ~/.zshrc</code>​</p><p>找到 plugins&#x3D;(git)</p><p>修改为 <code>plugins=(git z)</code>​</p><p>​<code>source ~/.zshrc</code>​ 保存后重新加载zsh配置</p><h4 id="使用效果"><a href="#使用效果" class="headerlink" title="使用效果"></a>使用效果</h4><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241736910.gif">​</p><h3 id="zsh-syntax-highlighting（错误提示插件）"><a href="#zsh-syntax-highlighting（错误提示插件）" class="headerlink" title="zsh-syntax-highlighting（错误提示插件）"></a>zsh-syntax-highlighting（错误提示插件）</h3><p>在输入命令的时候错误会，命令会变红提示</p><h4 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="加入plugin"><a href="#加入plugin" class="headerlink" title="加入plugin"></a>加入plugin</h4><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plugins=(git z zsh-syntax-highlighting)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="使用效果-1"><a href="#使用效果-1" class="headerlink" title="使用效果"></a>使用效果</h4><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241755628.gif">​</p><p>‍</p><h3 id="autojump（自动跳转插件）"><a href="#autojump（自动跳转插件）" class="headerlink" title="autojump（自动跳转插件）"></a>autojump（自动跳转插件）</h3><p>可以根据曾经cd过的目录，直接通过j &#x2F;dict 跳转进去</p><h4 id="安装-1"><a href="#安装-1" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install autojump</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="加入plugin-1"><a href="#加入plugin-1" class="headerlink" title="加入plugin"></a>加入plugin</h4><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plugins=(git z zsh-syntax-highlighting autojump)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="使用效果-2"><a href="#使用效果-2" class="headerlink" title="使用效果"></a>使用效果</h4><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241801335.gif">​</p><p>‍</p><p><em>还有很多好用的插件可以自行探索</em></p><p>‍</p><h1 id="Ubuntu-Regolith-3-0-效果演示"><a href="#Ubuntu-Regolith-3-0-效果演示" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu Regolith 3.0 效果演示"></a>Ubuntu Regolith 3.0 效果演示</h1><h2 id="使用帮助"><a href="#使用帮助" class="headerlink" title="使用帮助"></a>使用帮助</h2><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241809969.gif">​</p><h3 id="完整帮助图片"><a href="#完整帮助图片" class="headerlink" title="完整帮助图片"></a>完整帮助图片</h3><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241811990.png">​</p><p>‍</p><h2 id="多窗口操作"><a href="#多窗口操作" class="headerlink" title="多窗口操作"></a>多窗口操作</h2><p>​<img src="https://hexo-19989hexo-1233-1310773284.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202401241815811.gif">​</p><p><strong>更多操作可自行探索</strong></p><p>‍</p>]]></content>
      
      
